Owned and operated by the Manuli Ryco Group, Fluiconnecto Ryco excels in the
management of fluids in hydraulic systems. We cater to various industries,
including mining, construction, agriculture, marine and oil & gas. The Group
continues to drive the hydraulic and fluid conveyance industry forward with
our high-quality products, technical expertise and global reach.

** The Role **

The primary objective in this position is to provide ERP system support and
ensure uninterrupted day to day use of the sage 300 ERP and related systems
through user guidance, problem analysis and effective issue resolution

  * Provide 1st level ERP system support 
  * Ensure ERP related processes and procedures are up to date 
  * Resolve ERP user assistance requests relating to system and module functionality 
  * Assist with testing and implementation of new and modified functionality and reporting 
  * Ensure the integrity and accuracy of the ERP system data and information. 
  * Track and maintain the status of support requests 
  * Conduct remote ERP usage training sessions for new and existing users 

** Experience, Knowledge and Skills **

  * Good knowledge of Sage 300 ERP core and supporting 3rd party systems 
  * Crystal Reports development experience 
  * Excellent problem solving skills 
  * Strong accounting knowledge 

** Why Join Us: **

** Well-established- ** Take pride in working for a long-standing world leader in the manufacturing hydraulic industry. 

** Professional development ** \- Full training is provided in this role, along with support from an experienced team 

** Social Culture ** \- Enjoy working with a close-knit team and supportive management. 

